                    </div>
                    <span>I loved this book...I read the blurb in the bookshop and thought it would be a nice sort of romance. It turned out to be much more than that...I recommend this novel to anyone!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A good read</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
